NUMBER 2352
NAME High tunnel
CAVE
DARKNESS

*DESCRIPTION_START
The passage runs down, down, down, away from the arch and into the heart of
the mountain. It is wide and has a high ceiling, plenty of room for a dragon
to fly along, small or large. A shelf of rock along the right wall is
stacked with the skulls of humans, aelfen and drakins, mounted as a mute
warning against any who would come here.
*DESCRIPTION_END

