NUMBER 2353
NAME High tunnel
CAVE
DARKNESS

*DESCRIPTION_START
What waits in the darkness? Something that breathes... you can hear it, air
whooshing in, out, a draft that changes direction. And yet you see nothing
that could do such a thing, only two walls, a ceiling and the scalloped,
sloping floor, all of unliving stone.
*DESCRIPTION_END

