NUMBER 2354
NAME Antechamber
CAVE
DARKNESS

EXIT U 2353

*DESCRIPTION_START
Shadows cluster in the corners of this chamber, real corners fashioned by
civilized stoneworkers. There is no doubt at all that this is an artificial
tunnel now, highlander work perhaps. The shadows seem to watch you, though
they show no sign of movement or life. A massive door is set into the stone
wall, covered with writing in a tongue you do not understand.
*DESCRIPTION_END

