NUMBER 2364
NAME Lair, low-ceilinged room
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS

*DESCRIPTION_START
This chamber has a ceiling within easy reach, though its walls are quite
some distance apart, a wafer-like shape the overall result. At one end of
the room is a portcullis with a torch sconce on either side.
*DESCRIPTION_END


