NUMBER 2366
NAME Cave chamber
DEEPCAVE
DARKNESS

*DESCRIPTION_START
Colors glitter from the walls of this cave, streaks of blue and yellow and
fiery green. While the ceiling is hung with stalactites in many colors, the
floor is smooth and looks fairly comfortable. An archway leads south, but
beyond that there is no exit. A pool, shallow but not clear, fills one
corner of the cavern.
*DESCRIPTION_END

EXIT S 2365

